categories: Category:Commerce and labor guilds and unions

nodes.text: The Corellian Shipbuilders Union operated during the time of the Galactic Civil War. Jadam Questrel was the Union's official representative in Doaba Guerfel on Corellia, and the head of the Guild of Non-Human Skilled Laborers, the Herglic Kijo Mnuue, had some contacts within the union.
